text:
{key:Static, muted}
{trigger:breach} The opponent breached discards cards from the top of their deck equal to Marlita Yellow's {force:?}
{trigger:enter} Discard the top 5 cards of your deck.

{key:Quick}
{cost:As an additional cost, sacrifice a card you control.}
{trigger:victor} You may clone Nyx.

{key:Delayed}
You may cast Radiant Larva if it enters the discard without perishing.
{trigger:cast} Set a Bug card from your deck or discard except it is LVL 1.

{key:delayed}
{trigger:enter} Void 3 cards from the top of your deck.
{trigger:perish} Add up to 2 of the voided cards to your hand.

{key:Bleed, Doom}
Horror From Above's {force:?} is equal to the number of times you've played it this turn times 2.
{trigger:victor} Return Horror From Above to your Hand.

{key:instant, static}
{cost:As an additional cost, sacrifice 2 cards you control.}
{trigger:enter} Reveal cards from the top of your deck equal to your LVL, then add up to 1 card of each LVL among them to your hand. You cannot play the cards this turn. Send the rest to the bottom of your deck.

{key:Warden, Delayed}
{cost:As an additional cost, you must control at least 3 cards.} Whenever a non-token card you control perishes except Ouroboros, you may void a card from your hand and return it to play.
{trigger:perish} Return Ouroboros to your hand.

{key:Quick}
{trigger:victor} Create a Bead {force:1}/{key:fragile} token with "{trigger:perish} A Ghost card you control gains {force:1}". You may move Spiritual Warlord to an open zone on your grid. If you do, Spiritual Warlord remains active.
{trigger:breach} Draw cards equal to the damage dealt by Spiritual Warlord.

{key:static, warden, safe}
{trigger:end} Sacrifice a card you control.
{trigger:breach} Set a unit from your discard.

{key:muted}
{trigger:enter} Attach all Crow cards in play to Crow Devourer.
{trigger:breach} Deal damage to the opponent equal to the number of Crow cards attached to Crow Devourer.

{key:delayed}
When you cast your first 2 cards in a turn, draw a card.
{trigger:enter} Discard your hand.

{key:Bleed}
{cost:As an additional cost, sacrifice 2 cards you control.}
{trigger:enter} Cards you control gain {key:bleed}.
{trigger:cast} Destroy all non-Bug units in play.

{key:bleed}
{cost:As an additional cost, set your life to 1.} 
{trigger:victor} You may destroy a card in play.
{trigger:breach} Gain {force:1}.

{key:Static}
{cost:As an additional cost, sacrifice a card you control.}
{trigger:perish} If Hive Infiltrator does not have {key:fragile}, return it to play as {force:2} with {key:fragile} and {key:delayed}.
{trigger:breach} If Hive Infiltrator has {key:fragile}, remove it and gain {force:1}.

{key:Delayed, Immortal, Bleed, Static}
{cost:As an additional cost, sacrifice 2 cards you control. Must be played in the center zone.}
{trigger:perish} Destroy all units in play.
{trigger:begin} Sacrifice a unit you control.

{key:sealed, muted, immortal}
Toxician cannot gain {key:sick}.
{trigger:begin} Up to 2 target cards gain {key:sick}.
